text: Ülker Pamir (born 7 June 1913, date of death unknown) was a Turkish alpine skier. He competed in the men's combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1913 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Turkish male alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Turkey Category:Alpine skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
